sections.heading: Transmission, telephone, and telegraph lines; violations; penalty
sections.text: Any person who violates any of the provisions of sections 75-709 to 75-724 shall be guilty of a Class II misdemeanor.SourceLaws 1963, c. 425, art. VII, ยง 23, p. 1428;Laws 1977, LB 39, ยง 206;Laws 1993, LB 121, ยง 474;Laws 1994, LB 414,
